50 692 m 545 692 l S
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 675 Td (1. Purpose & Scope) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 657 Td (Governs all planned and emergency changes to Safaricom Ethiopia live network infrastructure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 644 Td (Applies to all domains: RAN, Transmission, Core PS/CS, and Power Systems.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 623 Td (2. Change Categories) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 605 Td (• Standard Change \(SC\): Pre-approved, low-risk, repeatable. No CAB approval required.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 592 Td (• Normal Change \(NC\): Requires full CAB review. Minimum 5-business-day lead time.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 579 Td (• Emergency Change \(EC\): P1/P2 incident-driven. Expedited CAB approval within 2 hours.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 558 Td (3. CR Submission Requirements) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 540 Td (• Submit CR via ITSM portal with full technical justification and rollback plan.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 527 Td (• Mandatory fields: Impact assessment, risk rating, test plan, rollback procedure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 514 Td (• Attach vendor/OEM technical note for all hardware changes.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 493 Td (4. CAB Review Process) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 475 Td (• Weekly CAB meeting: every Tuesday 14:00 EAT.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 462 Td (• Emergency CAB: convened within 2 hours via NOC bridge call.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 449 Td (• All domain heads must be present or provide written delegate authority.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 428 Td (5. Change Execution) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 410 Td (• Implement only during approved maintenance window.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 397 Td (• NOC L1 operator on standby throughout execution.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 384 Td (• Real-time monitoring mandatory during and 30 min post-implementation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 371 Td (• Rollback decision must be made within agreed window if KPIs degrade >5%.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 350 Td (6. Post-Change Review) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 332 Td (• Verify all KPIs returned to pre-change baseline within 1 hour.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 319 Td (• Update CMDB with all configuration changes made.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 306 Td (• Close CR in ITSM with implementation notes and outcome documented.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 50 30 Td (CONFIDENTIAL — For internal NOC use only. Safaricom Ethiopia PLC.) Tj ET
